  <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;8:6" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-simple-map-w-reltable.dita">The following example contains the markup for a simple relationship table:</p>
  <codeblock class="+ topic/pre pr-d/codeblock " xml:space="preserve" xtrc="codeblock:1;9:14" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-simple-map-w-reltable.dita">&lt;map&gt;
&lt;!-- ... --&gt;
&lt;reltable&gt;
  &lt;relheader&gt;
    &lt;relcolspec type="concept"/&gt;
    &lt;relcolspec type="task"/&gt;
    &lt;relcolspec type="reference"/&gt;
  &lt;/relheader&gt;
  &lt;relrow&gt;
    &lt;relcell&gt;
      &lt;topicref href="A.dita"/&gt;
    &lt;/relcell&gt;
    &lt;relcell&gt;
      &lt;topicref href="B.dita"/&gt;
    &lt;/relcell&gt;
    &lt;relcell&gt;
      &lt;topicref href="C1.dita"/&gt;
      &lt;topicref href="C2.dita"/&gt;
    &lt;/relcell&gt;
  &lt;/relrow&gt;
&lt;/reltable&gt;
&lt;/map&gt;</codeblock>
  <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;31:6" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-simple-map-w-reltable.dita">A DITA-aware tool might represent the relationship table graphically:<simpletable class="- topic/simpletable " xtrc="simpletable:1;31:88" xtrf="file:/C:/Git/dita/specification/archSpec/base/example-simple-map-w-reltable.dita">
